narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Learn about how to write a senior thesis, talk through yours, get advice and feedback. Very helpful.
Yeah cuz it's required for a year-long thesis, which is definitely worth writing.

Research can be overwhelming but you'll learn a lot in this class. Everything is rather independent but often times your classmates will have a lot of great advice, so listen to them. And don't do anything last minute!
